---
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
const { name, subtitle } = Astro.props;
---

<section
  id="interests"
  class="relative w-full min-h-[70vh] flex flex-col justify-center bg-center bg-cover overflow-hidden"
  style="
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0)),
      linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0)),
      linear-gradient(to bottom, black 0%, black 20px),
      url('/fondo-interests.jpg');
    background-size: cover, cover, 100% 20px, cover;
    background-position: center, center, bottom, center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat, no-repeat, no-repeat, no-repeat;
  "
>
  <div class="section-content flex flex-col items-center text-center px-4 py-16 md:py-24 max-w-6xl w-full">

    <!-- TÃ­tulo -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-12 title-futuristic">
      Other Interests
    </h2>

    <article class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3 w-full">

      <!-- Healthy Lifestyle & Science -->
      <Card className="flex flex-col transform transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        <img src="src/assets/healthy.jpg" alt="Healthy Lifestyle" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-4 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110" />
        <h3 class="card-title mb-2">Healthy Lifestyle & Science</h3>
        <p class="card-text mb-2">
          I love maintaining a healthy and active lifestyle. Running is one of my favorite ways to challenge myself and push my limits.
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
          I am fascinated by science and passionate about continuous learning. Teaching and guiding people allows me to communicate complex ideas clearly, combining curiosity with inspiration.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <!-- Cooking & Gardening -->
      <Card className="flex flex-col transform transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        <img src="src/assets/cuisine.jpg" alt="Cooking & Gardening" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-4 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110" />
        <h3 class="card-title mb-2">Cooking & Gardening</h3>
        <p class="card-text mb-2">
          Cooking is a way to explore cultures and create memories. Improvising dishes helps me connect with my experiences.
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
          Gardening aromatic herbs recently has complemented my cooking, bringing freshness and personal touch to my meals.
        </p>
      </Card>

      <!-- Video Games & Creativity -->
      <Card className="flex flex-col transform transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        <img src="src/assets/rpg.png" alt="RPG Game" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-4 transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-110" />
        <h3 class="card-title mb-2">Video Games & Creativity</h3>
        <p class="card-text mb-2">
          Video games allow me to unleash creativity. In Minecraft, I build cities and transportation networks, expanding my virtual world.
        </p>
        <p class="card-text">
          Developing a Viking-inspired RPG lets me design a universe, create characters, improve drawing, pixel art, map-making, and storytelling skills.
        </p>
      </Card>

    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .card-title {
    color: #40E0D0;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .card-text {
    color: #b9b9b9;
  }
</style>
